{
  "page": "Marra Rogare",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Marra Rogare</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_114_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">114&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nor after <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Marra Rogare</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> noble banking family. She was the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Magister_for_Life\" title=\"First Magister for Life\">First Magister</a> of Lys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marra_Rogare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Marra was the daughter of Lysandro Rogare. She had six brothers, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysaro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysaro Rogare\">Lysaro</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Moredo_Rogare\" title=\"Moredo Rogare\">Moredo</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lotho_Rogare\" title=\"Lotho Rogare\">Lotho</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Drako_Rogare\" title=\"Drako Rogare\">Drako</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Fredo_Rogare\" title=\"Fredo Rogare\">Fredo</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Roggerio_Rogare\" title=\"Roggerio Rogare\">Roggerio</a>, and two sisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Larra_Rogare\" title=\"Larra Rogare\">Larra</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lysara_Rogare\" title=\"Lysara Rogare\">Lysara</a>, as well as sixteen bastard siblings.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the death of her father, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro \"the Magnificent\"</a>, Marra inherited his library. When the <a href=\"/index.php/Rogare_Bank\" title=\"Rogare Bank\">Rogare Bank</a> ran dry in <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a>, Lysaro Rogare's brothers and sisters claimed to have no part in it, but many doubted their claims of innocence. She claimed sanctuary at the Temple of <a href=\"/index.php/Yndros_of_the_Twilight\" title=\"Yndros of the Twilight\">Yndros</a> in man's garb. When the Rogares were tried, Marra was deprived of the books she had inherited.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marra_Rogare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px seri